I feel it in the water.

4
00:00:41,580 --> 00:00:44,520
我从地上感觉到
I feel it in the earth.

5
00:00:46,090 --> 00:00:49,080
我从空气中嗅到
I smell it in the air.

6
00:00:49,490 --> 00:00:51,390
