魔  戒

10
00:01:09,810 --> 00:01:14,180
这一切都从铸造魔戒开始
It began with the forging of the Great Rings.

11
00:01:14,380 --> 00:01:16,280
精灵族得到三只戒指
Three were given to the Elves.

12
00:01:16,450 --> 00:01:20,250
他们长生不老 也是最有智慧最公平的种族
Immortal,wisest and fairest of all beings.

13
00:01:21,320 --> 00:01:23,380
矮人族分到七只戒指
Seven to the Dwarf-lords.

14
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:28,560
他们很会挖掘矿坑 是山洞的能工巧匠
Great miners and craftsmen of the mountain halls.

15
00:01:29,030 --> 00:01:30,260
而九只
And nine...

16
00:01:30,460 --> 00:01:33,460
九只戒指送给了人类
...nine rings were gifted to the race of Men...

17
00:01:33,700 --> 00:01:37,530
他们比别人更渴望权力
... who,above all else,desire power.

18
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:38,600
(中土世界)

19
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:43,870
每只戒指都拥有统治每个种族的力量
For within these rings was bound the strength and will to govern each race.

20
00:01:45,380 --> 00:01:48,540
但他们都受到了欺骗
But they were all of them deceived.

21
00:01:48,780 --> 00:01:50,870
因为还有另一只被铸造了
For another ring was made.

22
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:55,280
在魔多末日火山的烈焰中
In the land of Mordor,in the fires of Mount Doom...

23
00:01:55,720 --> 00:02:00,260
黑暗魔君索伦暗中铸造了一只至尊魔戒
... the Dark Lord Sauron forged in secret a Master Ring...

24
00:02:00,390 --> 00:02:02,320
来控制一切
... to control all others.

25
00:02:02,630 --> 00:02:06,590
他在至尊魔戒中注入他的邪恶 残酷
And into this Ring he poured his cruelty,his malice...

26
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:11,000
以及支配天下的可怕欲望
...and his will to dominate all life.

27
00:02:11,970 --> 00:02:15,870
一只统治一切的至尊魔戒
One Ring to rule them all.

28
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:18,370
一个接一个...
One by one...

29
00:02:18,580 --> 00:02:23,240
中土世界的自由之土感受到了至尊魔戒的力量
... the Free Lands of Middle-earth fell to the power of the Ring.

30
00:02:23,450 --> 00:02:26,480
但是有些人群起反抗
But there were some who resisted.

31
00:02:26,950 --> 00:02:31,720
人类和精灵组成了最后的同盟对抗魔多的邪恶兵团
A Last Alliance of Men and Elves marched against the armies of Mordor.

32
00:02:31,820 --> 00:02:36,650
他们在险恶的末日火山为中土世界的自由奋战
And on the slopes of Mount Doom,they fought for the freedom of Middle-earth.

33
00:02:49,210 --> 00:02:50,130
稳住阵线！
Tangado haid!

34
00:02:51,830 --> 00:02:53,420
放箭！
Leithio i philinn!

35
00:03:06,790 --> 00:03:09,420
胜利终于在望
Victory was near.

36
00:03:14,170 --> 00:03:15,930
但是至尊魔戒的力量
But the power of the Ring...

37
00:03:16,740 --> 00:03:18,170
无人能敌
...could not be undone.

38
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:44,700
就在这时候
It was in this moment...

39
00:03:44,900 --> 00:03:47,260
当大家都失去希望之际
... when all hope had faded...

40
00:03:47,500 --> 00:03:51,600
人皇之子埃西铎拾起他父亲的宝剑
... that Isildur,son of the king,took up his father's sword.

41
00:04:22,700 --> 00:04:29,200
黑暗魔君索伦 中土世界自由人民之敌终于被击败
Sauron,the enemy of the Free Peoples of Middle-earth,was defeated.

42
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:38,240
至尊魔戒落入埃西铎手中
The Ring passed to Isildur...

43
00:04:38,450 --> 00:04:42,650
他只有一次机会永远摧毁邪恶
... who had this one chance to destroy evil forever.

44
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:45,520
但是人心
But the hearts of Men...

45
00:04:45,730 --> 00:04:48,220
很容易受到蛊惑
...are easily corrupted.

46
00:04:48,460 --> 00:04:53,090
而且至尊魔戒有它自己的意志
And the Ring of Power has a will of its own.

47
00:05:18,290 --> 00:05:20,920
它背叛了埃西铎
It betrayed Isildur...

48
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:25,160
最后害死了他
... to his death.

49
00:05:29,340 --> 00:05:33,200
不该被遗忘的东西
And some things that should not have been forgotten...

50
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:35,770
也遗忘了
... were lost.

51
00:05:36,610 --> 00:05:38,800
历史成为传说
History became legend...

52
00:05:39,010 --> 00:05:41,000
传说成为神话
...legend became myth.

53
00:05:41,210 --> 00:05:44,110
两千五百年来
And fortwo and a half thousand years...

54
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:47,980
至尊魔戒的下落无人得知
... the Ring passed out of all knowledge.

55
00:05:48,620 --> 00:05:51,450
直到机会到来
Until,when chance came...

56
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:55,220
让它蛊惑一个新的持有者
...it ensnared a new bearer.

57
00:05:56,600 --> 00:06:01,400
我的宝贝
My precious.

58
00:06:01,670 --> 00:06:04,190
至尊魔戒落入咕噜手中
The Ring came to the creature Gollum...

59
00:06:04,370 --> 00:06:08,310
他把它带到迷雾山脉的洞穴中
... who took it deep into the tunnels of the Misty Mountains.

60
00:06:08,610 --> 00:06:11,470
他的身心完全被魔戒占据
And there it consumed him.

61
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,700
它落到我手中
It came to me.

62
00:06:13,910 --> 00:06:18,350
我的 我的爱 是我的
My own. My Iove. My own.

63
00:06:18,550 --> 00:06:23,250
我的宝贝
My precious.

64
00:06:26,890 --> 00:06:30,330
魔戒让咕噜得到违反自然的长寿
The Ring brought to Gollum unnatural long life.

65
00:06:30,530 --> 00:06:34,360
五百年来它扭曲他的心智
For 500 years it poisoned his mind.

66
00:06:34,570 --> 00:06:39,160
它在咕噜阴暗的洞穴中静静地等待着
And in the gloom of Gollum's cave,it waited.

67
00:06:39,370 --> 00:06:42,640
黑暗再度笼罩大地
Darkness crept back into the forests of the world.

68
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:45,710
谣传东方升起邪恶力量
Rumor grew of a shadow in the East...

69
00:06:45,910 --> 00:06:48,710
人们心中产生无名的恐惧
... whispers of a nameless fear.

70
00:06:48,910 --> 00:06:52,210
于是至尊魔戒知道
And the Ring of Power perceived...

71
00:06:52,420 --> 00:06:55,220
它即将再度现身
...its time had now come.

72
00:06:57,660 --> 00:07:00,280
它舍弃了咕噜
It abandoned Gollum.

73
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:05,450
但是出乎至尊魔戒的意料之外
But something happened then the Ring did not intend.

74
00:07:06,300 --> 00:07:10,890
它被一个最料想不到的人捡到
It was picked up by the most unlikely creature imaginable.

75
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:12,160
这是什么？
What's this?

76
00:07:12,370 --> 00:07:13,800
一个哈比人
A Hobbit.

77
00:07:13,970 --> 00:07:16,740
夏尔的比尔博・巴金斯
Bilbo Baggins of the Shire.

78
00:07:16,940 --> 00:07:18,710
一只戒指
A ring.

79
00:07:18,910 --> 00:07:20,780
不见了！
Lost!

80
00:07:23,550 --> 00:07:26,990
我的宝贝不见了！
My precious is Iost!

81
00:07:27,220 --> 00:07:29,480
不久的将来...
For the time will soon come...

82
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:34,920
哈比人将决定世界的命运
... when Hobbits will shape the fortunes of all.

83
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,430
(瑞文戴尔)

84
00:07:39,700 --> 00:07:42,760
9月的第22天
The 22nd day of September...

85
00:07:42,940 --> 00:07:44,160
1400年
...in the year 1 400...

86
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:45,960
(哈比屯)

87
00:07:46,340 --> 00:07:48,100
以夏尔历法计算
...by Shire-reckoning.

88
00:07:48,140 --> 00:07:49,130
(夏尔)

89
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:53,240
哈比屯西区 巴榭路 袋底洞
Bag End,Bagshot Row,Hobbiton,Westfarthing...

90
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,270
(伊利雅德)

91
00:07:54,780 --> 00:07:56,810
夏尔
...the Shire...

92
00:07:56,980 --> 00:07:59,820
中土世界
...Middle-earth.

93
00:08:04,460 --> 00:08:07,790
世界第三纪元
The Third Age of this world.

94
00:08:10,580 --> 00:08:15,170
护 戒 使 者

95
00:08:19,340 --> 00:08:23,430
去而复返
There and Back Again.'

96
00:08:23,980 --> 00:08:25,810
哈比人的故事
A Hobbit's Tale.

97
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:28,510
比尔博・巴金斯著
By Bilbo Baggins.

98
00:08:28,710 --> 00:08:31,980
（去而复返：哈比人的故事 比尔博・巴金斯著）

99
00:08:34,650 --> 00:08:36,380
现在...
Now...

100
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:39,110
该从何说起呢？
...where to begin?

101
00:08:40,390 --> 00:08:41,450
对了
Ah,yes....

102
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:47,800
关于...
"Concerning...

103
00:08:47,930 --> 00:08:48,870
（关于哈比人）

104
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:50,490
哈比人
...Hobbits."

105
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:55,260
哈比人一直都在夏尔的四个区开垦种植 安居乐业
Hobbits have been living and farming in the four Farthings of the Shire...

106
00:08:55,340 --> 00:08:57,330
数百年来
...for many hundreds of years...

107
00:08:57,510 --> 00:09:00,480
都乐于遗忘并被世人遗忘
...quite content to ignore and be ignored...

108
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:03,840
也就是世上的其他人种
...by the world of the Big Folk.

109
00:09:04,220 --> 00:09:09,850
毕竟中土世界充满不计其数的奇怪生物
Middle-earth being,after all,full of strange creatures beyond count...

110
00:09:10,020 --> 00:09:13,220
哈比人的存在微不足道
...Hobbits must seem of little importance...

111
00:09:13,390 --> 00:09:17,420
他们并非骁勇善战的勇士
...being neither renowned as great warriors...

112
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:21,790
也不算是聪明绝顶的智者
...nor counted among the very wise.

113
00:09:26,170 --> 00:09:29,160
佛罗多！有人敲门
Frodo! Someone at the door.

114
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:32,940
事实上 有人说
In fact,it has been remarked by some...

115
00:09:33,110 --> 00:09:37,550
哈比人唯一真正热爱的就是食物
... that Hobbits' only real passion is for food.

116
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:40,110
但这是很不公平的说法
A rather unfair observation...

117
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:43,950
因为我们也很喜欢酿麦酒
...as we have also developed a keen interest in the brewing of ales...

118
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:47,120
还有抽烟草
...and the smoking of pipe-weed.

119
00:09:47,590 --> 00:09:50,430
但是我们内心的真爱
But where our hearts truly lie...

120
00:09:50,630 --> 00:09:52,720
就是和平宁静
...is in peace and quiet...

121
00:09:53,430 --> 00:09:55,630
还有肥沃的土地
...and good,tilled earth.

122
00:09:55,830 --> 00:10:00,970
每一个哈比人都热爱种植生长的东西
For all Hobbits share a love of things that grow.

123
00:10:04,140 --> 00:10:08,550
别人一定会觉得我们的日子过得太悠闲
And,yes,no doubt to others,our ways seem quaint.

124
00:10:08,710 --> 00:10:13,950
但是今天更是印证了我的想法
But today of all days,it is brought home to me.'

125
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:20,490
能过朴实简单的生活真的是一种幸福
It is no bad thing to celebrate a simple life.

126
00:10:20,490 --> 00:10:22,150
（生日快乐比尔博・巴金斯）

127
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:27,860
佛罗多 开门！
Frodo,the door!

128
00:10:31,670 --> 00:10:33,600
讨厌 那小子呢？
Sticklebacks. Where is that boy?

129
00:10:33,770 --> 00:10:35,470
佛罗多！
Frodo!

130
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:44,810
外面风景多美丽
Down from the door where it began

131
00:10:49,590 --> 00:10:53,390
我要踏上这旅程
And I must follow if I can

132
00:10:54,390 --> 00:10:58,490
眼前道路无止尽
The road goes ever on and on

133
00:10:58,700 --> 00:11:02,160
蜿蜒崎岖又漫长
Down from the door where it began

134
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:07,340
虽然路程尚遥远
Now far ahead the road has gone

135
00:11:08,010 --> 00:11:10,870
我必须继续前进
And I must follow if I can

136
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:11,770
你迟到了
You're late.

137
00:11:15,050 --> 00:11:18,850
巫师绝对不会迟到 佛罗多・巴金斯
A wizard is never late,Frodo Baggins.

138
00:11:19,650 --> 00:11:24,280
他也不会早到 他一定是按照计划准时到
Nor is he early. He arrives precisely when he means to.

139
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:38,690
见到你太好了 甘道夫！
It's wonderful to see you,Gandalf!

140
00:11:42,570 --> 00:11:46,310
我怎么会错过你比尔博叔叔的生日？
You didn't think I'd miss your Uncle Bilbo's birthday?

141
00:11:48,010 --> 00:11:50,140
那老不死还好吧？
How is the old rascal?

142
00:11:50,680 --> 00:11:54,210
我听说生日宴会非常盛大
I hear it's going to be a party of special magnificence.

143
00:11:54,390 --> 00:11:56,880
你也了解比尔博 他把这儿搞得鸡飞狗跳
You know Bilbo. He's got the whole place in an uproar.

144
00:11:57,020 --> 00:11:58,990
这样他应该高兴了
Well,that should please him.

145
00:11:59,160 --> 00:12:01,020
夏尔有一半人都被邀请了
Half the Shire's been invited.

146
00:12:01,260 --> 00:12:03,890
另外一半也不请自来
And the rest of them are turning up anyway.

147
00:12:07,070 --> 00:12:10,400
夏尔的生活就这样继续着
And so life in the Shire goes on...

148
00:12:10,570 --> 00:12:13,600
从古到今都一样
... very much as it has this past Age...

149
00:12:13,770 --> 00:12:19,340
自给自足 快乐幸福 没有什么太大的改变
...full of its own comings and goings,with change coming slowly.

150
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:21,410
或许永远也不会有所改变
If it comes at all.

151
00:12:22,680 --> 00:12:26,120
因为夏尔的一切历久弥新
For things are made to endure in the Shire...

152
00:12:26,290 --> 00:12:29,780
一代一代地传下去
...passing from one generation to the next.

153
00:12:30,220 --> 00:12:35,180
巴金斯家族一直都有成员住在山丘下的
There's always been a Baggins living here under the Hill...

154
00:12:35,390 --> 00:12:36,730
袋底洞
...in Bag End.

155
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:42,260
以后也一定会有
And there always will be.

156
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:46,400
不过说实话 最近比尔博有点怪
To tell you the truth,Bilbo's been a bit odd lately.

157
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:49,870
我是说 比以前更怪
I mean,more than usual.

158
00:12:50,910 --> 00:12:52,770
他成天把自己关在书房
He's taken to Iocking himself in his study.

159
00:12:54,180 --> 00:12:58,640
我每次趁他不注意都看到他在研究古地图
He spends hours poring over old maps when he thinks I'm not looking.

160
00:13:11,260 --> 00:13:12,920
它跑哪儿去了？
Where's it gone?

161
00:13:39,590 --> 00:13:41,820
他一定在搞什么名堂
He's up to something.

162
00:13:49,970 --> 00:13:51,860
好吧 你不说拉倒
All right,then. Keep your secrets. 

163
00:13:51,970 --> 00:13:52,460
什么？
What?

164
00:13:52,670 --> 00:13:54,370
我知道你一定脱不了关系
But I know you have something to do with it.

165
00:13:54,640 --> 00:13:55,660
真是的
Good gracious me.

166
00:13:56,040 --> 00:13:58,970
在你出现前 巴金斯家族一向都很规矩
Before you came along,we Bagginses were very well thought of.

167
00:13:59,140 --> 00:13:59,970
确实
Indeed.

168
00:14:00,210 --> 00:14:02,810
我们从不冒险或做意外的事
Never had any adventures or did anything unexpected.

169
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:08,990
如果你指的是关于龙的那件事 我只是勉强牵涉
If you're referring to the incident with the dragon,I was barely involved.

170
00:14:09,190 --> 00:14:12,780
我所做的只是轻轻地把你叔叔推出门外
All I did was give your uncle a Iittle nudge out of the door.

171
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:17,090
不管怎样你都被正式列为捣乱份子
Whatever you did,you've been officially labeled a disturber of the peace.

172
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:19,330
真的吗？
Oh,really?

173
00:14:25,040 --> 00:14:26,970
甘道夫！甘道夫！
Gandalf! Gandalf!

174
00:14:33,150 --> 00:14:34,340
放烟火 甘道夫
Fireworks,Gandalf!

175
00:14:37,420 --> 00:14:40,040
甘道夫！放烟火 甘道夫！
Gandalf! Fireworks,Gandalf!

176
00:14:58,900 --> 00:14:59,930
甘道夫？
Gandalf?

177
00:15:00,540 --> 00:15:02,340
你回来了我好高兴
I'm glad you're back. 

178
00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:04,640
我也是 好孩子
So am I,dear boy.

179
00:15:09,050 --> 00:15:10,880
我也是
So am I.

180
00:15:37,350 --> 00:15:39,580
（与晚会无关者免进）

181
00:15:42,710 --> 00:15:44,150
不要 谢谢！
