Birds,beasts.

562
00:43:25,210 --> 00:43:27,040
它安全吗？
Is it safe?

563
00:43:28,710 --> 00:43:30,080
千万别戴上它
Never put it on...

564
00:43:30,280 --> 00:43:33,720
黑暗魔君的爪牙会被它的力量吸引来
...for the agents of the Dark Lord will be drawn to its power.

565
00:43:33,880 --> 00:43:35,370
