566
00:43:35,890 --> 00:43:39,050
至尊魔戒想要回到主人手上
...the Ring is trying to get back to its master.

567
00:43:39,420 --> 00:43:41,720
它想要被找到
It wants to be found.

568
00:44:22,130 --> 00:44:24,330
这就是了
This is it.

569
00:44:24,670 --> 00:44:26,800
这是什么？
This is what?

570
00:44:27,140 --> 00:44:29,200
我只要再跨一步
If I take one more step...

571
00:44:29,710 --> 00:44:33,610
就是我离家最远的一次
...it'll be the farthest away from home I've ever been.

572
00:44:37,810 --> 00:44:39,300
走吧 山姆
Come on,Sam.

573
