"It's a dangerous business,Frodo." 

575
00:44:52,360 --> 00:44:55,560
一旦出了门 你踏步上了路
"Going out your door,You step onto the road.

576
00:44:55,630 --> 00:44:58,570
如果你不继续前进
and if you don't keep your feet...

577
