They're leaving Middle-earth.

587
00:45:45,400 --> 00:45:47,740
永远不再回来
Never to return.

588
00:45:50,690 --> 00:45:52,690
不知道为什么
I don't know why...

589
00:45:53,490 --> 00:45:55,860
我会感到这么悲伤
...it makes me sad.

590
00:45:57,890 --> 00:46:02,560
我躺到哪儿都有树根顶着我的背
Everywhere I lie there's a dirty great root sticking into my back.

591
00:46:03,270 --> 00:46:05,030
闭上眼睛
Just shut your eyes...

592
00:46:05,200 --> 00:46:07,970
想像着你躺在自己的床上
...and imagine you're back in your own bed...

593
00:46:08,140 --> 00:46:12,070
柔软的床垫和舒服的羽毛枕头
...with a soft mattress and a Iovely feather pillow.

594
00:46:21,380 --> 00:46:24,080
