It's not working,Mr. Frodo.

595
00:46:24,250 --> 00:46:27,120
我在荒郊野外永远都睡不着
I'm never going to be able to sleep out here.

596
00:46:29,460 --> 00:46:31,830
我也睡不着 山姆
Me neither,Sam.

597
00:47:00,320 --> 00:47:03,420
末日火山升起硝烟
Smoke rises from the Mountain of Doom.

598
00:47:03,590 --> 00:47:05,250
时间不多了
The hour grows late.

599
00:47:05,430 --> 00:47:08,990
灰袍巫师甘道夫赶到艾辛格
And Gandalf the Grey rides to Isengard...

600
00:47:09,200 --> 00:47:11,630
寻求我的建议
...seeking my counsel.

601
00:47:11,840 --> 00:47:15,830
你就是为了这件事来找我？
For that is why you have come,is it not?

602
00:47:16,010 --> 00:47:17,300
我的老朋友
My old friend.

603
00:47:17,610 --> 00:47:19,170
萨鲁曼
Saruman.

604
00:47:23,980 --> 00:47:25,670
你确信如此吗？
You are sure of this? 

605
00:47:25,680 --> 00:47:26,970
确信不疑
Beyond any doubt.

606
00:47:27,620 --> 00:47:30,120
那么说至尊魔戒被发现了
So the Ring of Power has been found.

607
00:47:30,290 --> 00:47:33,480
这么多年来 它一直在夏尔
All these Iong years,it was in the Shire.

608
00:47:33,690 --> 00:47:35,490
就在我鼻子底下
Under my very nose. 

609
00:47:35,590 --> 00:47:37,190
而你却没有智慧看出它
Yet you did not have the wit to see it.

610
00:47:37,490 --> 00:47:42,400
你喜欢的半身人的烟草很明显地熏坏了你的头脑
