But we still have time. Time enough to counter Sauron if we act quickly.

612
00:47:47,000 --> 00:47:48,490
时间？
Time?

613
00:47:49,470 --> 00:47:52,100
我们哪来的时间？
What time do you think we have?

614
00:47:52,510 --> 00:47:56,380
索伦的力量几乎完全恢复
Sauron has regained much of his former strength.

615
00:47:56,550 --> 00:47:58,810
虽然他尚未完全复生
He cannot yet take physical form...

616
00:47:58,980 --> 00:48:01,680
但他的灵魂仍有强大魔力
...but his spirit has Iost none of its potency.

617
00:48:02,350 --> 00:48:07,420
虽然他被封在要塞中 但是他却无所不知
Concealed within his fortress,the Lord of Mordor sees all.

618
00:48:07,990 --> 00:48:13,930
他的视线能穿透乌云 阴影 土地甚至肉体
His gaze pierces cloud,shadow,earth and flesh.

619
00:48:15,430 --> 00:48:18,560
你知道我在说什么 甘道夫
You know of what I speak,Gandalf.

620
00:48:19,500 --> 00:48:24,740
一个被烈焰包围的巨大眼晴
A Great Eye,Iidless,wreathed in flame.

621
00:48:25,710 --> 00:48:27,510
索伦之眼
The Eye of Sauron.

622
00:48:27,710 --> 00:48:30,270
他正在聚集邪恶力量
He is gathering all evil to him.

623
00:48:30,710 --> 00:48:35,580
很快 他就能召集大军向中土世界展开攻击
Very soon,he'll have summoned an army great enough for an assault upon Middle-earth.

624
00:48:35,920 --> 00:48:38,290
你知道这些？
You know this?

625
00:48:38,860 --> 00:48:40,350
怎么会？
How?

626
00:48:40,920 --> 00:48:42,590
我已经看到了
I have seen it.

627
00:48:43,030 --> 00:48:46,220
真知晶球是个危险的东西 萨鲁曼
A palantir is a dangerous tool,Saruman.

628
00:48:46,930 --> 00:48:48,420
为什么？
Why?

629
00:48:48,900 --> 00:48:51,600
为什么我们要害怕使用它？
Why should we fear to use it?

630
00:48:54,240 --> 00:48:58,230
其它的真知之石下落不明
They are not all accounted for,the lost Seeing-stones.

631
00:48:58,410 --> 00:49:01,610
我们不知道有谁也在看
We do not know who else may be watching.

632
00:49:04,210 --> 00:49:06,940
时间比你想的还迟
The hour is later than you think.

633
00:49:07,120 --> 00:49:09,450
索伦已经在行动
Sauron's forces are already moving.

634
00:49:11,520 --> 00:49:14,650
那九个已经离开米那斯魔窟
The Nine have Ieft Minas Morgul.

635
00:49:14,820 --> 00:49:15,880
