The Nine?

636
00:49:16,060 --> 00:49:19,120
他们在仲夏夜跨越艾辛河
They crossed the River Isen on Midsummer's Eve...

637
00:49:19,300 --> 00:49:21,960
伪装成黑骑士
...disguised as riders in black.

638
00:49:22,200 --> 00:49:23,430
他们已经到了夏尔？
They've reached the Shire? 

639
00:49:23,600 --> 00:49:26,130
他们会找到至尊魔戒
They will find the Ring.

640
00:49:27,770 --> 00:49:29,970
然后杀死它的持有者
And kill the one who carries it.

641
00:49:30,470 --> 00:49:31,960
