Frodo!

642
00:49:44,590 --> 00:49:48,990
你不会真的以为哈比人能对抗索伦吧？
You did not seriously think that a Hobbit could contend with the will of Sauron?

643
00:49:49,760 --> 00:49:52,520
谁都无法对抗他
There are none who can.

644
00:49:55,030 --> 00:49:57,800
反抗魔多的力量...
Against the power of Mordor...

645
00:49:57,970 --> 00:50:00,600
