...there can be no victory.

646
00:50:02,540 --> 00:50:05,740
我们必须投靠他 甘道夫
We must join with him,Gandalf.

647
00:50:07,010 --> 00:50:09,340
我们必须投靠索伦
We must join with Sauron.

648
00:50:12,020 --> 00:50:14,680
这么做才聪明 我的朋友
It would be wise,my friend.

649
00:50:15,150 --> 00:50:16,640
