Tell me...

650
00:50:16,820 --> 00:50:17,840
朋友...
...friend...

651
00:50:18,860 --> 00:50:23,380
智者萨鲁曼几时发疯了？
...when did Saruman the Wise abandon reason for madness?

652
00:51:02,900 --> 00:51:04,590
我给了你机会...
I gave you the chance...

653
00:51:05,740 --> 00:51:08,400
自愿帮助我...
...of aiding me willingly...

654
00:51:09,040 --> 00:51:13,210
