...but you have elected the way of pain!

655
00:51:36,070 --> 00:51:37,560
佛罗多先生？
Mr. Frodo?

656
00:51:38,130 --> 00:51:39,930
佛罗多？佛罗多！
Frodo? Frodo!

657
00:51:41,370 --> 00:51:42,700
我以为把你跟丢了
I thought I'd lost you. 

658
00:51:42,870 --> 00:51:44,600
