What did he say?

661
00:51:48,610 --> 00:51:52,480
“紧跟着他 山姆卫斯・詹吉” 我会紧跟着你
"Don't you lose him,Samwise Gamgee." And I don't mean to.

662
00:51:52,750 --> 00:51:56,380
